    83→  {
    84→    question: 'What widgets are available?',
    85→    answer: 'Over 44 widgets including: Weather, News feeds, Calculator, World Clock, Pomodoro Timer, Quick Notes, Calendar, Task Summary, Time Tracking stats, Bookmarks, and many more. New widgets are added regularly.',
    86→  },
    87→  // Time Tracking & Calendar
    88→  {
    89→    question: 'How does time tracking work?',
    90→    answer: 'Go to Time Tracking in the sidebar. Start the timer when you begin work, assign it to a project, and stop when done. View daily/weekly stats, generate reports, and export to CSV for invoicing.',
    91→  },
    92→  {
